  CONTAINED SECTIONS IMPLEMENTATION EXAMPLE

  To add contained sections support to any section:

  1. Add the settings to your section schema:
  In your section's schema, copy the JSON from snippets/contained-sections-settings.liquid
  (Note: Don't use liquid render tags in schema - copy the actual JSON content)

  2. Wrap your section content:
  Option A - Wrap everything:

  {% render 'contained-sections-wrapper', section: section %}
    <div class="section">
      <!-- Your existing section content -->
    </div>
  {% endrender %}

  Option B - Open/close separately for more control:

  {% render 'contained-sections-wrapper', section: section, action: 'open' %}
  <div class="section">
    <!-- Your existing section content -->
  </div>
  {% render 'contained-sections-wrapper', action: 'close' %}

  3. Example section with contained sections:

  <div class="section-{{ section.id }}-padding">
    {% render 'contained-sections-wrapper', section: section, action: 'open' %}

    <div class="page-width">
      <div class="section-header">
        {% if section.settings.title != blank %}
          <h2 class="title">{{ section.settings.title }}</h2>
        {% endif %}
      </div>

      <div class="section-content">
        <!-- Your section content here -->
      </div>
    </div>

    {% render 'contained-sections-wrapper', action: 'close' %}
  </div>

  4. Available variant classes (automatically applied based on settings):
  - contained-section--compact (smaller padding/margin)
  - contained-section--spacious (larger padding/margin)
  - contained-section--full-width (no side margins)
  - contained-section--light (light color theme)
  - contained-section--dark (dark color theme)
  - contained-section--accent (accent color theme)
  - contained-section--no-border (removes border)
  - contained-section--thick-border (thicker border)
  - contained-section--dashed-border (dashed border style)
  - contained-section--no-shadow (removes shadow)
  - contained-section--heavy-shadow (stronger shadow)
  - contained-section--sharp (no border radius)
  - contained-section--rounded (extra border radius)
  - contained-section--pill (pill-shaped)
  - contained-section--no-hover (disables hover animation)

  5. Manual class application (if not using snippets):

  <div class="contained-section contained-section--spacious contained-section--accent">
    <!-- Your content -->
  </div>

  Note: The contained sections system must be enabled in Theme Settings > Contained Sections
  for any of these features to work.
{% endcomment %}

